===Glyph origin===
{{Han etyl}}
{{liushu|p}} – pictographic representation of a field divided into four sections. See the original version of [[甫]] and [[里]].
Sometimes it means mask. See [[異]] and [[鬼]]. Unrelated to [[思]], [[黄]], [[果]], [[由]], [[甲]], and perhaps [[番]].

